cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper proposes an approach for depth estimation in multi-view stereo using deep learning. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The approach involves learning to match and triangulate a small set of interest points, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions interest point detection and descriptor learning, which are common techniques in computer graphics (cs.GR).
